title: Ep 44 - Limitations Are Optional
itunes:title: Ep 44 - Limitations Are Optional
description:
Limitations are optional. Almost everything that holds us back from our dreams are limitations and fears made up in our own minds. In this episode we talk about how to overcome limitations and rise above our fears in order to live the life of our dreams.
